        "body": "Green loan review is manual: an analyst reads the application, checks it against EU Taxonomy thresholds and LMA Green Loan Principles by hand, and the whole cycle takes 10-12 days. Built for the LMA EDGE Hackathon 2026, where the brief was to make that review fast without making it careless.",
